sops.sop:
Workflow:
1. User -> Transportation Planner;
2. Transportation Planner -> Accommodation Planner 
   Transportation Planner -> Restaurant Planner 
   Transportation -> Attractions Planner (in parallel);
3. Accommodation Planner, Restaurant Planner, Attractions Planner -> Plan Checker;
4. Plan Checker -> Final Plan Summarizer;
5. Final Plan Summarizer -> End.

Description:
First, the Transportation Planner determines two Texas cities to visit and establishes the transportation sequence between Baton Rouge -> City A -> City B -> Baton Rouge across 5 days. This framework defines daily locations for other planners. Accommodation, Restaurant, and Attractions Planners then work in parallel to find options matching the solo traveler's needs. The Plan Checker performs comprehensive validation including budget adherence (critical for $2300 constraint) and logistical consistency. Finally, the Final Plan Summarizer compiles all verified components into a cohesive itinerary with precise details.
